event_text: As a storm rages across the beach and waves crash upon the shore, m_c is tucked up in the healer den, {PRONOUN/m_c/poss} sleep anything but restful. {PRONOUN/m_c/subject/CAP} {VERB/m_c/keep/keeps} seeing flashes of prophecy_list_sight. {PRONOUN/m_c/subject/CAP} {VERB/m_c/wake/wakes} with a shiver, wondering what {PRONOUN/m_c/poss} dreams mean for the Clan.
The things {PRONOUN/m_c/subject} saw today: omen_list_sight... m_c dips a paw in a rockpool, watching the tiny, crawling life inside, and considering what the omens foretell.
